---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { apps } from '~/data/apps.generated';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Teach with Spark & Anvil"
  description="Become a Spark & Anvil teacher. Keep 100% of your class fees (we take 0%; Stripe ~3% direct). No curriculum to build, no marketing to do. Live small-group classes for ages 9-14 using our 135 apps."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-12">
    <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 mb-4 bg-forge text-warm text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider rounded-full">Now Recruiting — 501(c)(3) Early Pilot</span>
    <h1 class="font-brand font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-anvil dark:text-warm mb-4">
      Teach the apps your students already love.<br />
      <span class="text-forge">Keep 100%.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
      Spark &amp; Anvil is a 501(c)(3) non-profit teacher network for live, small-group classes — using our
      {apps.length} portfolio apps as the curriculum. We pre-define every class slot from a specific app's
      curriculum and grade band. You bid on slots that match your expertise. You teach.
      <strong>You keep 100% of every dollar</strong> (minus the ~3% Stripe processing fee — same as any payment
      processor). <strong>We take 0% — ever.</strong>
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <a href="mailto:teachers@spark-and-anvil.com?subject=Spark%20%26%20Anvil%20Early%20Teacher%20Pilot" class="btn-primary">Apply to the early pilot</a>
      <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn-secondary">How it works</a>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-anvil/60 dark:text-warm/60 italic">
      First 50 partners get paid pilot classes + founder access during 2026. 100% of class fees go directly to you.
      Stripe Connect Direct Charges — same as any payment processor.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Earnings comparison -->
  <section class="bg-anvil/5 dark:bg-warm/5 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="font-brand font-bold text-3xl text-anvil dark:text-warm mb-8">Earnings comparison</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-anvil/40 rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-anvil/15 dark:border-warm/20">
          <h3 class="font-brand font-bold text-xl text-anvil/60 dark:text-warm/60 mb-2">Outschool</h3>
          <div class="text-5xl font-brand font-bold text-anvil/60 dark:text-warm/60 mb-4">70<span class="text-2xl">%</span></div>
          <p class="text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">to teacher (after Outschool's 30% take)</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 space-y-1">
            <li>• Source your own materials</li>
            <li>• Market your own classes</li>
            <li>• Handle COPPA compliance yourself</li>
            <li>• Generic Zoom integration</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-forge text-warm rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-forge">
          <h3 class="font-brand font-bold text-xl text-warm mb-2">Spark &amp; Anvil</h3>
          <div class="text-5xl font-brand font-bold text-warm mb-4">100<span class="text-2xl">%</span></div>
          <p class="text-warm/90 leading-relaxed mb-4">to teacher (we take 0%; Stripe ~3% direct)</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-warm/90 space-y-1">
            <li>• <strong>{apps.length} apps</strong> as your curriculum</li>
            <li>• <strong>Curated slots</strong> with built-in parent demand</li>
            <li>• <strong>We handle COPPA-2025</strong> + parental consent + state laws</li>
            <li>• <strong>ForgeClassroom</strong>: live cohort sync + teacher dashboard + AI co-pilot</li>
            <li>• <strong>501(c)(3) non-profit</strong> — platform funded by foundations + donors</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-anvil/40 rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-anvil/15 dark:border-warm/20">
          <h3 class="font-brand font-bold text-xl text-anvil/60 dark:text-warm/60 mb-2">Khan Academy / Code.org</h3>
          <div class="text-5xl font-brand font-bold text-anvil/60 dark:text-warm/60 mb-4">N/A</div>
          <p class="text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">no live-class marketplace; teacher = user / volunteer</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 space-y-1">
            <li>• Free apps for teachers</li>
            <li>• No live-class paid model</li>
            <li>• Volunteer or unpaid only</li>
            <li>• Different model than ours</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-anvil/60 dark:text-warm/60">
        On a $20/student/class × 4-student cohort × 8 weeks ($640 gross):
        <strong>You earn ~$622</strong> with Spark &amp; Anvil (after Stripe's ~$18 processing fee — paid
        directly by you to Stripe, not deducted by us) vs <strong>$448</strong> on Outschool.
        <strong>That's $174 more per cohort — and the difference compounds across multiple cohorts.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How it works -->
  <section id="how-it-works" class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h2 class="font-brand font-bold text-3xl text-anvil dark:text-warm mb-8">How it works</h2>
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-forge text-warm rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-brand font-bold text-xl">1</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-brand font-bold text-xl text-anvil mb-2 dark:text-warm">Browse open class slots</h3>
          <p class="text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 leading-relaxed">
            We define each slot from a specific app + grade band + curriculum standard.
            Example: <em>"GambitTales: Sir Pinwell's Tactical Patterns (Grades 5–6) — 6 weeks × 1 hour/week,
            suggested rate $15–25/student."</em>
            All slots are pre-curated by us; you focus on teaching, not class design.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-forge text-warm rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-brand font-bold text-xl">2</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-brand font-bold text-xl text-anvil mb-2 dark:text-warm">Bid on the slots you want</h3>
          <p class="text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 leading-relaxed">
            Pick your hourly rate (within range), your weekly availability, and your qualifications.
            We review against the slot's requirements. Top teachers get premier slots.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-forge text-warm rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-brand font-bold text-xl">3</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-brand font-bold text-xl text-anvil mb-2 dark:text-warm">Parents enroll students into your cohort</h3>
          <p class="text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 leading-relaxed">
            We market the slot to families who already use the app. You walk into a full
            cohort of 4–6 motivated students. No cold-start; no marketing burden.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-forge text-warm rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-brand font-bold text-xl">4</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-brand font-bold text-xl text-anvil mb-2 dark:text-warm">Teach with ForgeClassroom integration</h3>
          <p class="text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 leading-relaxed">
            Each app has built-in classroom features: live cohort sync (everyone on the same lesson),
            real-time teacher dashboard, AI co-pilot suggesting discussion prompts, auto-generated
            weekly parent reports. You teach; we handle the tech.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-forge text-warm rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-brand font-bold text-xl">5</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-brand font-bold text-xl text-anvil mb-2 dark:text-warm">Get paid weekly via Stripe Connect</h3>
          <p class="text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 leading-relaxed">
            Stripe Connect Direct Charges — you are the merchant of record, you receive the parent's
            payment directly, you pay Stripe's standard ~2.9% + $0.30 processing fee (same as any
            payment processor). <strong>Spark &amp; Anvil collects $0.</strong> 1099-K issued by
            Stripe at year-end. <strong>No platform commission, ever.</strong>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How we sustain the platform -->
  <section class="bg-anvil/5 dark:bg-warm/5 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="font-brand font-bold text-3xl text-anvil dark:text-warm mb-4">How we sustain the platform</h2>
      <p class="text-anvil/80 dark:text-warm/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Spark &amp; Anvil is a 501(c)(3) non-profit (pending). Our teacher network platform —
        COPPA compliance, background-check coverage, ForgeClassroom server, parent-side discovery,
        payment orchestration — costs about $50K-$140K per year to operate. We cover those costs
        through foundation grants (Chan-Zuckerberg Initiative, Hewlett, Schmidt Sciences program
        lines) and individual donations from families who value the mission. Want to help sustain
        teacher-fee-free live classes for kids ages 9-14?
      </p>
      <a href="/donate?source=teach&tier=teacher-network-sustainers" class="btn-primary">
        Support the teacher network →
      </a>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-anvil/60 dark:text-warm/60">
        Donate at /donate or join our Teacher Network Sustainers monthly giving tier.
        Your gift is tax-deductible to the full extent of US law.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pilot details -->
  <section class="bg-spark/10 dark:bg-spark/15 py-16 border-y border-spark/30 dark:border-spark/40 dark:border-spark/50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="font-brand font-bold text-3xl text-anvil mb-4 dark:text-warm">Early pilot — first 50 partners</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-anvil/80 dark:text-warm/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We're recruiting the first 50 teachers to pilot Spark &amp; Anvil classrooms during 2026. Each pilot partner gets:
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-anvil/80 dark:text-warm/80 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        <li>✅ <strong>Free background check</strong> (we cover it — funded by founding-pilot donors)</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>Founder access</strong>: direct Slack channel with our team for feedback + roadmap input</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>Featured Early Teacher badge</strong> on your public profile (parent-visible)</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>30 paid pilot classes</strong> at full $15–25/student rates (100% to you)</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>Priority slot selection</strong> when the public teacher network launches Q1 2027</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>Founding Sustainer recognition</strong> on the /donate page if you wish to be acknowledged (optional — we'll never publish your name without consent)</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="mailto:teachers@spark-and-anvil.com?subject=Spark%20%26%20Anvil%20Early%20Teacher%20Pilot%20Application&body=Please%20share%3A%0A%0A1.%20Name%20%2B%20teaching%20background%3A%0A2.%20Subject%20specialties%20(math%2Fliteracy%2Fchess%2FSEL%2Fetc.)%3A%0A3.%20Outschool%20%2F%20other%20marketplace%20experience%3A%0A4.%20Best%20Outschool%20class%20you%20taught%20(if%20applicable)%3A%0A5.%20Link%20to%20sample%20teaching%20video%20(optional)%3A%0A6.%20Availability%20for%20a%2015-min%20intro%20call%3A%0A%0A" class="btn-primary">Apply now</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h2 class="font-brand font-bold text-3xl text-anvil dark:text-warm mb-8">Common questions</h2>
    <dl class="space-y-6">
      <div>
        <dt class="font-brand font-bold text-lg mb-2">Why does Spark &amp; Anvil take 0%? How is the platform sustained?</dt>
        <dd class="text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 leading-relaxed">
          We're a 501(c)(3) non-profit. Our mission is to keep educational software + live classes
          accessible without extracting a commission from teachers. Platform costs (~$50K-$140K/yr)
          are covered by foundation grants (CZI Learning Commons, Hewlett OER, Schmidt Sciences) and
          individual donations. Your class fees go directly to you. That's the model.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt class="font-brand font-bold text-lg mb-2">What about Stripe's fee? Are there hidden costs?</dt>
        <dd class="text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 leading-relaxed">
          Stripe charges ~2.9% + $0.30 per transaction — that's the standard for any payment
          processor. You pay it directly to Stripe. We don't add anything to it. There are no
          hidden costs, no annual platform fees, no per-cohort fees. The only deduction from your
          earnings is Stripe's standard processing fee, paid directly to Stripe.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt class="font-brand font-bold text-lg mb-2">Compared to TeachersPayTeachers or Outschool, what's the catch?</dt>
        <dd class="text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 leading-relaxed">
          No catch — we're a different kind of organization. TeachersPayTeachers (a marketplace
          for static content) and Outschool (a marketplace for live classes) take 15-30% commissions
          because they're for-profit companies that need that revenue. We're a non-profit that
          covers platform costs through philanthropy. The catch (if you want to call it that) is
          our slots are curated from our app curriculum — you don't get to invent any class topic.
          That trade-off lets us offer 100%-to-teacher economics.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt class="font-brand font-bold text-lg mb-2">When does the public teacher network launch?</dt>
        <dd class="text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 leading-relaxed">
          <strong>Q1 2027.</strong> Early pilot (paid contracts for 50 teachers) starts Q3 2026.
          Apply now to lock in your pilot slot.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt class="font-brand font-bold text-lg mb-2">Do I need a teaching credential?</dt>
        <dd class="text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 leading-relaxed">
          A state teaching license is preferred but not required for most slots. Subject expertise + sample
          teaching reel + background check (we pay) + parent reviews establish your standing on the platform.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt class="font-brand font-bold text-lg mb-2">Can I design my own custom slots?</dt>
        <dd class="text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 leading-relaxed">
          <strong>Yes — Tier 2 feature.</strong> Top teachers (5+ successful cohorts) can propose custom slot templates.
          Approved templates give you exclusive first-run + ongoing royalty share. Curated slots remain the default
          to maintain quality and brand cohesion.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt class="font-brand font-bold text-lg mb-2">What's the time commitment for the pilot?</dt>
        <dd class="text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 leading-relaxed">
          30 paid pilot classes over ~3–4 months (typical ~2-3 hours/week). Stipend is paid up-front; classes
          earn additional per-class income at full rates.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt class="font-brand font-bold text-lg mb-2">Can my existing Outschool students transfer to my Spark &amp; Anvil cohorts?</dt>
        <dd class="text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 leading-relaxed">
          Yes — we'll help you import your roster + give you a co-branded landing page to share with families.
          Parents can sign up directly; their kids' Spark &amp; Anvil app progress will sync automatically into
          your teacher dashboard.
        </dd>
      </div>
    </dl>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <a href="mailto:teachers@spark-and-anvil.com?subject=Spark%20%26%20Anvil%20Early%20Teacher%20Pilot" class="btn-primary">Apply to the early pilot</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
